snippet.title: Arjun Katuwal - Teri Meri Kahani (Official Music Video) Nimesh Shrestha || Barsha kshetri || Vague
snippet.description:
This song is a humble tribute to the beautiful but heartbreaking love story of Bibek Pangeni and Srijana Subedi ‚Äî a couple who showed the world what true love, courage, and devotion really look like.
Their journey reminded us that love is not just about the smiles we share, but also the battles we fight together, hand in hand.
It is our way of honoring a love that touched millions and continues to inspire people everywhere.

To Bibek ‚Äî your strength and smile will never be forgotten.
To Srijana ‚Äî your love and dedication remain a timeless example of what it means to stand by someone with your whole heart.

snippet.description:
Look out. #Supergirl lands in theaters June 26.

‚ÄúSupergirl,‚Äù DC Studios‚Äô newest feature film to hit the big screen, will be in theaters worldwide this summer from Warner Bros. Pictures, starring Milly Alcock in the dual role of Supergirl/Kara Zor-El.  Craig Gillespie directs the film from a screenplay by Ana Nogueira.

When an unexpected and ruthless adversary strikes too close to home, Kara Zor-El, aka Supergirl, reluctantly joins forces with an unlikely companion on an epic, interstellar journey of vengeance and justice.

Alcock stars alongside Matthias Schoenaerts, Eve Ridley, David Krumholtz, Emily Beecham, and Jason Momoa.

DC Studios heads Peter Safran and James Gunn are producing the film, which is based on characters from DC, Supergirl based on characters created by Jerry Siegel and Joe Shuster.  The film is executive produced by Nigel Gostelow, Chantal Nong Vo and Lars P. Winther.  Behind the camera, Gillespie is joined by director of photography Rob Hardy, production designer Neil Lamont, editor Tatiana S. Riegel, costume designer Anna B. Sheppard, Visual Effects Supervisor Geoffrey Baumann, and composer Ramin Djawadi.  

DC Studios Presents a Troll Court Entertainment Production, The Safran Company Production, A Film by Craig Gillespie, ‚ÄúSupergirl,‚Äù which will be in theaters and IMAX¬Æ across North America on June 26, 2026, and internationally beginning 24 June 2026, distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures.

snippet.description:
Presenting the official teaser of One Two Cha Cha Chaa, starring Ashutosh Rana, Lalit Prabhakar, Anantvijay Joshi, Harsh Mayar, Nyrraa M Banerji, Abhimanyu Singh, Mukesh Tiwari, Ashok Pathak and Chittranjan Giri.

A mad, chaotic, laugh-riot entertainer from Pellucidar releasing in cinemas on 16 January 2026.

Step into a world of comedy, confusion, romance and full-on ‚ÄúCha Cha Chaa‚Äù energy!
This teaser gives you a glimpse of the madness, quirky characters, hilarious banter and high-voltage drama that awaits on the big screen.

#tukimusic  #pokhara #nephop 
TUKI MUSIC - Arajak (‡§Ö‡§∞‡§æ‡§ú‡§ï)


"Arajak (‡§Ö‡§∞‡§æ‡§ú‡§ï)" is a revolutionary song that captures the emotional turmoil relating to death of ‚ÄúGen Z ‚Äú protesters in Nepal. On 9 September 2025, protesters angered by government repression and corruption stormed the Nepalese Federal Parliament Building in Kathmandu. The protest escalated when the police killed 19 protesters including a 12-year-old child on 8 September 2025. Through this evocative lyrics and soulful melody, the song portrays frustration of Nepalese Youth towards corruption and political insanity.

"Arajak (‡§Ö‡§∞‡§æ‡§ú‡§ï)" is a revolutionary song that captures the emotional turmoil relating to death of ‚ÄúGen Z ‚Äú protesters in Nepal. On 9 September 2025, protesters angered by government repression and corruption stormed the Nepalese Federal Parliament Building in Kathmandu. Through this evocative lyrics and soulful melody, the song portrays frustration of Nepalese Youth towards corruption and political insanity.

snippet.description:
Provided To Youtube By Amal Star Media
| üïâ ||
Sanju Rathod presents 'Shaky' a Marathi track like no other!

Shaky is a fresh Marathi Pop anthem that blends playful Afrobeat grooves with everyday desi charm. Sanju Rathod and Isha Malviya bring effortless swag, catchy hooks, and vibrant energy in this fun, feel-good love track. A bold, danceable vibe that pushes Marathi music into exciting new territory.

Singer - Sanju Rathod
LyricsComposer - Sanju Rathod

snippet.title: India‚Äôs Biggest Blockbuster Is Back in cinemas ‚Äî ‚ÄòSholay - The Final Cut‚Äô 12th Dec release worldwide
snippet.description:
India‚Äôs Biggest Blockbuster Is Back in cinemas ‚Äî ‚ÄòSholay - The Final Cut‚Äô 12th Dec release worldwide

Presenting the trailer of Sholay: The Final Cut.
Restored in 4K & Dolby 5.1, and releasing on 12th December 2025, this is the first-ever theatrical presentation of the original uncut version. As we celebrate 50 years of Sholay, we are honoured to bring this timeless classic back to cinemas for audiences old and new.

Produced by Sippy Films ¬∑ Directed by Ramesh Sippy ¬∑ Restored by Film Heritage Foundation
Releasing theatrically via PEN Marudhar.

#SholayTheFinalCut #SholayOn12Dec #SholayTrailer

Film: Sholay (1975) | ‡§∂‡•ã‡§≤‡•á
Film cast : Amitabh Bachchan, Dharmendra, Hema Malini, Sanjeev Kumar, Amjad Khan, Jaya Bachchan, A K Hangal, Satyen Kappu, Mac Mohan, Sachin Pilgaonkar, Jagdeep, Asrani, Leela Mishra, Iftekhar, Om Shiv Puri, Viju Khote, Vikas Anand, Keshto Mukherjee, Mushtaq Merchant, Gita Siddharth, Helen, Jalal Aga, Birbal, Jairaj, Master Alankar, Raj Kishore, Sharad Kumar, Bhanumati, Rajesh, Darshan, Rajan Kapoor, Habib, Surender, Bhagwan Sinha, Jerry Dsouza, Kedar, Saigal, Rajeshwari, Krishna, Girija
Singer : Anand Bakshi, Bhupinder, Kishore Kumar, Lata Mangeshkar, Manna Dey, R D Burman
Lyricist : Anand Bakshi
Music Director : R D Burman, Basu Manohari, Maruti Rao
Film Director : Ramesh Sippy
Film Producer : G P Sippy

 In the village of Ramgarh, retired police chief Thakur Baldev Singh (Sanjeev Kumar) plots to bring down the notorious bandit Gabbar Singh (Amjad Khan) and enlists the help of two lesser criminals, Jai (Amitabh Bachchan) and Veeru (Dharmendra). When Gabbar attacks the village, however, Jai and Veeru wonder why Thakur does nothing to help them. They soon learn that he has no arms, and that Gabbar was the one who cut them off. Enraged by this, they redouble their efforts to help.

Managers: Shirsodhi Banerjee (@shirsodhi), Kartik Iyer (@kartik_iyer_)

Inaam Lyrics: 

Paragraph 1

Malum 
Hai na 
Hum janay 
Tumko tumse zyada

Tumko 
Mila hai woh
Saalon se 
Jo bhi hai manga

Pre-chorus 1

Kaise khilono ki 
Ro ro ke
Karte the mangay 

Ik bar mil jaye 
Do din mein
Hi bhul jatay  

Chorus 1

Lekin khilono ke dil 
Toh hote hi nahin the

Dil toh humara hai 
Janay galat kya sahi yeh

Kitna the chahte par
Ab tumko yaad na aatey 
Hum

Paragraph 2

Kya yaad tumko 
Tum humko
‚ÄòInaam‚Äô the kehte 

Karte the kitna kuch
Panay ki chah 
Mein pehlay 


Pre-chorus 2

Ab yeh inaam ka 
Tum pe ilzaam hai jana

Dil hai gawah
Jeete jabse ho
Tumko hai hara 

Chorus 2

Cheezein badalti hain 
Itna toh hum ne bhi mana

Itna badal jaogay 
Jana kisne tha jana  

Jo tha parvana 
Ab usko humari parwah na 
Kyun?

Pre-Bridge

Dil mein baat kya hai?
Haan bolo humse 

Chahta aur kya hai? 
Haan bolo humse

Kya kami yahan hai?
Haan bolo humse na

Jo kaha mila hai
Haan bolo humse 

Badle mein bhala hai
Haan bolo humse

Manga tumse kya hai
Hai manga zara sa hi, kya hi, 

Kya? haye

Bas 

Bridge

Jo khat likhe the tumne 
Unhe padh bhi lo zara 
Waadein kiye the jo bhi
Nibhao na aise kabhi

In waadon ki siyahi 
Abhi sukhi hi kahan?
Hai tumhari hi likhai
Yaan bhule ho ye bhi?

Paragraph 3

Kehne ko 
Wah wah 
Tum phir se 
Inaam ho jeete 

Chehre par
Muskan 
Par ankhein hain
Khush na kahin se 

Pre-chorus 3

Humne kaha tha
Hum janey tumko 
Tumse zyada 

Shayad galat the 
Par itna toh 
Humne hai jana 

Chorus 3

Har woh inaam 
Qadar ke bina hi hai waise 

Ghar mein padhe, 
Dhul khate khilono ke jaise

Pal bhar behlaye 
Par dil ko yeh khush na kar paye 
Yoon

Hidden verse

Ghar bethe likhta tha 
Dil ki kahani meri 

Charon taraf thi deewarein 
Deewaron se hi 

Kehta tha ik din 
Jahaan hoga haathon mein hi

Aa aa

Jo tha gumnamo mein 
Ab woh inaamon pe bhi 

Qaidi hai, Qaid hi hai 
Phir bhi dewaron mein hi 

Namumkin khwabon mein
Na khush udane meri 

Aa aa

snippet.title: Timi Merai [Timro Lagi]- Neetesh Jung Kunwar (Official Audio W Lyrics)
snippet.description:
This time, I dedicate this song to the one who picks me up every single time I fall. I may not be good with my words but that won't change my love and respect for you. Thank you for making me humble and wiser. 
Slowly and Steadily.


Listen on Spotify-

https://open.spotify.com/track/7yeA5sz8pPBkEaUnH7WuCR?si=bVJN7XnIQHKiM3Sj6r6fMA

Listen on Apple Music-

https://music.apple.com/np/album/timi-merai-single/1857765272

Available on Instagram, Tiktok and Facebook.

To all the lovers who're struggling with life's unknown forces, I wish this song brings you closer to each other.

#timrolagi

snippet.title: Aankhama Chasma Chyattai - Roj Moktan | Jamuna Yonjan | Amir Dong | Bipashna | Nisha | Kuisang
snippet.description:
A brand-new fusion of Selo and Nadhing Selo arrives with the energetic creation ‚ÄúAankhama Chasma Chyattai.‚Äù This special version carries emotion, rhythm, and nostalgia as Roj Moktan and Jamuna Yonjan lend their voices together after 20 long years, creating a powerful moment of musical reunion.

The lyrics, written by Jivan Bomjan Tamang and Roj Moktan, pair seamlessly with the music composed by Roj Moktan, giving the song a modern heartbeat while preserving its cultural depth.

The music video features dynamic performances by Amir Dong, Bipashna Tamang, Nisha Lama, and Kuisang Rumba, each adding expressive storytelling that enhances the flow and feeling of the song.

Guided by the direction of Amir Dong, the visuals carry a strong sense of culture, emotion, and cinematic style, resulting in a compelling and memorable presentation.

This music video is exclusively available on Roj Moktan‚Äôs Official YouTube Channel, with no reuploads or distribution permitted on any other platforms.

en.description:
A brand-new fusion of Selo and Nadhing Selo arrives with the energetic creation ‚ÄúAankhama Chasma Chyattai.‚Äù This special version carries emotion, rhythm, and nostalgia as Roj Moktan and Jamuna Yonjan lend their voices together after 20 long years, creating a powerful moment of musical reunion.

The lyrics, written by Jivan Bomjan Tamang and Roj Moktan, pair seamlessly with the music composed by Roj Moktan, giving the song a modern heartbeat while preserving its cultural depth.

The music video features dynamic performances by Amir Dong, Bipashna Tamang, Nisha Lama, and Kuisang Rumba, each adding expressive storytelling that enhances the flow and feeling of the song.

Guided by the direction of Amir Dong, the visuals carry a strong sense of culture, emotion, and cinematic style, resulting in a compelling and memorable presentation.

snippet.title: Twin Strings Lounge - Sufiyana Sham 2 | SE 2 ‚Ä¢ EP 1
snippet.description:
After receiving overwhelming love on Sufiyana Shaam 1, we knew we had to bring this feeling back but deeper and more heartfelt. Presenting Sufiyana Shaam 2 a continuation of a moment that started with you all. This time, we wanted to create something that you can play on quiet evenings, long drives, or those nights when music speaks louder than words.

For Band Booking & Business Queries | Artkonnect +91 9643654363

‚Ä¢ A Twin Strings Production ‚Ä¢

Vocals/E Guitar: Manav
Acoustic Guitar: Sagar
Keyboard: Sahil
Zendrum: Mohit Deen

Directed and Edited by Twin Strings
Music by Twin Strings

Ft. Revati Khattar (weddingchoreographybyrevati)
 w/ Apoorva Singh & Arhana Jain

Special thanks to Arjun Lounge for the amazing clothes. (https://www.instagram.com/arjunloungestudio?igsh=cjk4aGFoeDNxeXpo) 

Audio Credits:
Additional Vocals: Ritik Bhardwaj, Isha Chakravorty
Drums: Vijay Kumar
Bass: Langmuansiam Naulak
Supporting Vocals : Aryan Bir
Tabla: Rohit Chawla
Dholak: Danish Sharma
Flute: Gautam Dayal
Violin & Cello: Sayan Sinha & Aliaksandra Bandarchuk (Gooseberry Ensemble)
Recorded, Produced, Mixed Mastered at TS Studio.

Video Team Credits:
A Twin Strings Production (in association w/ Shadow Craft Films)

DOP: Nitin Goyal Cam
Edit: Twin Strings
Edit Organise & Graphics : Nikunj Agrawal
Cinematographer: Imran Ansari
Associate Cinematographer: Vikas
Colorist: Imran Ansari
BTS: Krish
Production Controller: Azam Qureshi
Makeup: Jayanti

‚ÄúRatna‚Äù is a cherished Nepal Bhasa classic, originally written and created by the legendary Bishnu Jalmi and Krishna Man Dangol, and immortalized by the soulful voice of Juju Kaji Ranjit.
With utmost respect to the original creators, and inspired by the heartfelt reinterpretation by Raju Maharjan & Kutumba, we humbly present our small tribute to Ratna ‚Äî a sincere attempt to honor its heritage, express our gratitude, and celebrate the timeless soul of Newa music. 

Inspired By : https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oc6vKrJdjtA

snippet.title: Unstable SMP: The First King
snippet.description:
After the LAW's 1000 player army was slaughtered by Wemmbu and Flame, their leader, LettuceK held an emergency announcement... where he announced that he would be holding an election for King of Unstable. This is Unstable SMP: The First King. 

Like ParrotX2 and his Unstable SMP series, where he is escaping Paragon / Proton: Minecraft's Most Secure Prison, or got hunted by a Minecraft Player who doesn't exist. This is a new and original Minecraft idea like HermitCraft or Lifesteal with Wemmbu, FlameFrags, or Spoke. Survival is harder than Hardcore Minecraft because PVP is on.

Original Music by @tsynphonia 

People in this video: @TheobaldTheBird @LettuceK @wemmbumc @Dtowncat herobanenair @Kibaxmc pro4d @Lightisytic @qCxsh @TomLWSMC @nezoshoki @Imvenpu @loppezz @Twirps 

This is a video on the Unstable Universe: a staged Minecraft server where ParrotX2, Wemmbu, Spoke, and FlameFrags tell stories in Minecraft.

A Minecraft video made by Parrot or ParrotX2 on other platforms! Enjoy!
